def aggregate_month(SDFP):
    SDF = SDFP.copy()
    SDF.loc[:, 'month'] = SDF.index.month
    SDF.loc[:, 'year'] = SDF.index.year
    SDFagg = SDF.groupby(['year', 'month']).agg(np.mean)
    SDFagg = SDFagg.reset_index()
    SDFagg.loc[:, 'monthdate'] = [str(int(y)) + '-' + str(int(m)) + '-' + '01' for (y, m) in zip(SDFagg.year, SDFagg.month)]
    SDFagg.index = pd.to_datetime(SDFagg.monthdate)
    SDFagg.loc[:, 'newdatetime'] = [pd.to_datetime(dt.strptime(dt.strftime(x + timedelta(days=32), format='%Y-%m-%d')[:9] + '1', '%Y-%m-%d')) for x in SDFagg.index]
    SDFagg.index = SDFagg.newdatetime
    SDFagg.drop(['year', 'month', 'monthdate', 'newdatetime'], axis=1, inplace=True)
    SDFagg = SDFagg.fillna(method='bfill')
    return SDFagg

makenewdata = False
newdatafile = 'Composite_Index_Data_steelstocks.csv'
if path.exists(newdatafile) and not makenewdata:
    print "Found data file"
    G = pd.read_csv(newdatafile, index_col='Date', parse_dates=True)
else:
    print "Data File not found. Preparing..."
    # READ AND PREPARE DATA
    CIS = pd.read_csv('coal_ironore_turkishscrap_processed.csv', index_col='Date', parse_dates=['Date'])
    SMI = pd.read_csv('stock_market_indices.csv', index_col='Date', parse_dates=['Date'])
    AMM = pd.read_csv('AMM_pandas.csv', index_col=0, parse_dates=['Date'])
    IDX = SMI[['AMM_Busheling', 'HR coil']]

    end = '2017-06-20'
    start = '2001-07-26'
    # stock_symbols = [u'CMC', u'MT', u'SCHN', u'STLD', u'AKS', u'NUE', u'X', u'ASX\:SGM']
    get_px = lambda x: web.DataReader(x, 'google', start=start, end=end)['Close']
    STOCKS = pd.DataFrame({sym:get_px(sym) for sym in stock_symbols})

    STOCKS_AGG = aggregate_month(STOCKS)

    CIS = aggregate_month(CIS)
    IDX = aggregate_month(IDX)
    AMM = aggregate_month(AMM)

    G = IDX.join(AMM, how='left')
    G = G.join(CIS, how='left')
    G = G.join(STOCKS_AGG, how='left')
    G = G.fillna(method='ffill').fillna(method='bfill')

    usecols = [
        u'SteelBenchmarker Mainland China rebar $/tonne', 
        u'Aluminium Alloy LME official $/tonne Cash',
        u'Aluminium LME official $/tonne Cash',
        u'AMM_Busheling',
        u'HR coil',
        u'Iron_Ore',
        u'Turkish_Scrap',
        u'Coking_Coal'
    ]

    usecols += list(STOCKS_AGG.columns)
    G = G[usecols]
    G.to_csv(newdatafile, index_label='Date')
    print "made new data file", newdatafile

def plot_coefficients(lf, modelDF):
    cseries = pd.Series(lf.coef_)
    barp = cseries.plot.bar(figsize=(20, 10))
    barp.set_xticklabels(modelDF['Columns'], rotation=-90)
    barp.tick_params(labelsize=20)
    plt.show()


def qq_plot_residuals(y_test, y_pred_test):
    f = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
    stats.probplot(y_test-y_pred_test, dist="norm", plot=pylab)
    plt.title('residuals qq-plot', fontsize=18)
    pylab.show()


def scatter_actual_vs_predicted(y_test, y_pred_test, plot_title):
    mintest = min(y_test.min(), y_pred_test.min())
    maxtest = max(y_test.max(), y_pred_test.max())
    f = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
    plt.scatter(x=y_test, y=y_pred_test)
    plt.plot(np.arange(mintest, maxtest, 0.1), np.arange(mintest, maxtest, 0.1), 'r-')
    plt.title(plot_title, fontsize=18)
    plt.show()

def do_model(G, first_date, last_train_date, pre_normalize, lm_normalize, lm_fit_intercept, model_type='lasso', positive=True):

    if pre_normalize:
        GN = (G - G.mean()) / G.std()
        nmean = G['AMM_Busheling'].mean()
        nstd = G['AMM_Busheling'].std()
    else:
        GN = G.copy()
        nmean = 0.
        nstd = 1.

    GN = GN.loc[first_date:]
    # Correlation of full data
    corr_full = GN.corr().loc['AMM_Busheling']
    corr_full.name = 'corr_full'
    # Correlation of training + testing sets
    corr_trte = GN.loc[first_date:].corr().loc['AMM_Busheling']
    corr_trte.name = 'corr_trte'
    # Correlation of training set only
    corr_tr = GN.loc[first_date:last_train_date].corr().loc['AMM_Busheling']
    corr_tr.name = 'corr_tr'
    # Correlation of testing set only
    corr_te = GN.loc[last_train_date:].corr().loc['AMM_Busheling']
    corr_te.name = 'corr_te'

    All_corr_coeffs = pd.concat([corr_full, corr_trte, corr_tr, corr_te], axis=1).sort_values('corr_full', ascending=False)

    X = GN.drop('AMM_Busheling', axis=1)
    y = GN['AMM_Busheling']

    X_train = X.loc[:last_train_date]
    X_test = X.loc[last_train_date:]
    y_train = y.loc[:last_train_date]
    y_test = y.loc[last_train_date:]

    if model_type == 'lasso':
        scv = TimeSeriesSplit(n_splits=6)
        cvModel = lm.LassoCV(cv=scv, n_alphas=2000,
                             positive=positive, copy_X=True,
                             fit_intercept=lm_fit_intercept,
                             normalize=lm_normalize)
        cvModel.fit(X_train, y_train)

        CM = cvModel

        lf = lm.Lasso(alpha=cvModel.alpha_,
                      positive=positive,
                      fit_intercept=lm_fit_intercept,
                      normalize=lm_normalize)
        lf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    else:
        lf = lm.LinearRegression(fit_intercept=lm_fit_intercept, normalize=lm_normalize)
        lf.fit(X_train, y_train)
        
    modelDF = pd.DataFrame()
    modelDF['Columns'] = X_train.columns
    modelDF['Coeff'] = lf.coef_
    modelDF['Intercept'] = lf.intercept_
    sorted_coefficients = modelDF.sort_values('Coeff', ascending=False)


    y_pred_test = lf.predict(X_test).flatten()
    y_pred_train = lf.predict(X_train).flatten()
    y_pred_all = lf.predict(X).flatten()
    
    testDF = GN.loc[last_train_date:].copy()
    trainDF = GN.loc[:last_train_date].copy()
    hatDF = GN.copy()

    hatDF.loc[:, 'Prediction'] = y_pred_all
    testDF.loc[:, 'Prediction'] = y_pred_test
    trainDF.loc[:, 'Prediction'] = y_pred_train
    
    corr = np.corrcoef(y_test, y_pred_test)[0,1]
    r2_cc = corr ** 2
    mae = metrics.mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test)
    mae2 = mae * nstd
    evs = explained_variance_score(y_test, y_pred_test, multioutput='raw_values')[0]
    med_ae = median_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test)
    rmse = np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    rmse2 = rmse * nstd
    r2_cd = r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test)
    test_score = lf.score(X_test, y_test)
    train_score = lf.score(X_train, y_train)
    all_score = lf.score(X, y)
    scalar_results = pd.Series({'all_score': all_score,
                                'train_score': train_score,
                                'test_score': test_score,
                                'r2_cc': r2_cc,
                                'r2_cd': r2_cd,
                                'mae': mae,
                                'med_ae': med_ae,
                                'evs': evs,
                                'rmse': rmse,
                               'mae2': mae2,
                               'rmse2': rmse2})

    SC = sorted_coefficients
    ACC = All_corr_coeffs
    SC.index = SC.Columns
    SC.drop('Columns', axis=1, inplace=True)
    ACC = ACC.join(SC, how='left')
    SR = scalar_results
    
    odict = SR.to_dict()
    odict['ltd'] = last_train_date

    print fmt_string.format(**odict)
    
    def plot_actual_vs_predicted_all_data(hatDF, X, last_train_date):
        f = plt.figure(figsize=(20, 10))
        t = hatDF.AMM_Busheling        
        plt.plot(hatDF.index, hatDF.AMM_Busheling, label='act', lw=5)
        plt.plot(hatDF.index, hatDF.Prediction, label='pred', lw=5)
        plt.axvline(x=pd.to_datetime(last_train_date), color='darkred')
        plt.legend(fontsize=15)
        plt.show()
        
    
    t = plot_actual_vs_predicted_all_data(hatDF, X, last_train_date)
    plot_coefficients(lf, modelDF)
    scatter_actual_vs_predicted(y_test, y_pred_test, 'Testing Data Only')
    scatter_actual_vs_predicted(y, y_pred_all, 'All Data')
    qq_plot_residuals(y_test, y_pred_test)
    return scalar_results, ACC, sorted_coefficients
